4Geeks Academy offers a course called "Become a AI Machine Learning Engineer" that prepares students for a career in data science and machine learning. The course is designed for students with no previous knowledge and promises to help them build their first ML models in just 16 weeks. The course covers topics such as Python, SQL, Looker, Streamlit, and Statistics. Students learn to create predictive models using libraries like Pandas and Numpy, and explore algorithms like Close Neighbors and Decision Trees. They also have the opportunity to work on real-life cases and develop their own AI projects. The course is taught by experienced instructors, including Sayyed Nezhadi, Francesco Pugliese, and Manuel Mena. The classes are held three times a week and have a maximum class size of 12 students. Upon completion, students receive a recognized certificate. The course is available in both English and Spanish. For more information, visit https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning. stop.